  "detailed_description": "Kinese is a chill, meditative experience made specifically for VR. There's no score, no enemies to kill and no overt goal. Try to discover how you can influence the world around you, what rules surround that influence and what the ultimate limits of those rules are.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n Kinese explores concepts of wonder, scale and awe, and how these can be conveyed through the medium of Virtual Reality.",
